window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>The end has come.</b></p> <p>The balance is broken, the Gilded Amulet is lost, and Aileana has been taken. Never before has the outlook in the Four Kingdoms been so grim.</p> <p>Vowing to retrieve his bonded mate at whatever cost, Xander will not rest until she is found. Life and death rest in balance and fate is playing a dangerous game with their lives.</p> <p>Luckily, Xander is not alone. With the help of old and new friends, he journeys through Ithenmyr to find his mate before the Dragon Queen can destroy everything he holds dear.</p> <p>Aileana isn't the only one in danger. The Four Kingdoms are on the verge of collapse. No matter the cost, the balance must be righted before time runs out.</p> <p>This is their last stand.</p> <p><i>This Rapunzel retelling is a slow burn, enemies-to-lovers high fantasy romance, and it is filled with banter, fated mates, fake marriage, and world-building.</i> Of Shale and Smoke <i>is book five in The Ithenmyr Chronicles.</i> <i>This series is upper YA/NA and will have moderate steam as the series progresses.</i></p>"; 
